name: Day 14: Interactive Map
description:
Welcome to day 14 of 15 in the Figma prototype challenge! In this challenge we will be combining everything the last three days into a single map prototype with multiple methods of interaction. In the file you will find:

  1. A gif demonstrating the animation
  2. A workspace for you to build your prototype
  3. The built out prototype to use as reference


Feel free to follow the prompt and/or add any other cool elements to your prototype. Whatever you choose to do, don't forget to post a Remix or publish a new Community File with the tag FigmaPrototypeChallenge! Happy prototyping! ðŸŽ‰
